com.yworks.yfiles.utils

Class ObservableCollection<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.utils.ObservableCollection<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the elements contained in this collection.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICollection<T>, IEnumerable<T>, IObservableCollection<T>, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>

    public class ObservableCollection<T>
extends Object
implements IObservableCollection<T>, ICollection<T>
    A simple default implementation of an IObservableCollection that is backed by an ordinary Collection.
